 column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221; text_direction=&#8221;default&#8221;]\n<h1 data-start=\"166\" data-end=\"199\"><strong data-start=\"168\" data-end=\"199\">Fakedash Terms &amp; Conditions<\/strong><\/h1>\n<hr data-start=\"201\" data-end=\"204\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"206\" data-end=\"237\"><strong data-start=\"209\" data-end=\"235\">1. Acceptance of Terms<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"238\" data-end=\"388\">By using Fakedash services, you agree to these terms and conditions (the &#8220;Terms&#8221;). If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use our services.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"393\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"395\" data-end=\"432\"><strong data-start=\"398\" data-end=\"430\">2. Subscription and Payments<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"827\">\n<li data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"550\">\n<p data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"550\">By subscribing to Fakedash services, you authorize recurring billing according to the selected subscription plan.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"625\">\n<p data-start=\"553\" data-end=\"625\">Subscription fees are charged at the beginning of each billing period.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"738\">\n<p data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"738\">All payments are processed automatically by <strong data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"682\">Stripe<\/strong> based on the subscription\u2019s status and billing cycle.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"739\" data-end=\"827\">\n<p data-start=\"741\" data-end=\"827\">Subscriptions remain active and billable until they are formally canceled by the user.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"832\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"834\" data-end=\"874\"><strong data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"872\">3. Cancellation of Subscription<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"1373\">\n<li data-start=\"875\" data-end=\"988\">\n<p data-start=\"877\" data-end=\"988\">You may cancel your subscription at any time through your account settings or by contacting our support team.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1154\">\n<p data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1154\">Canceling a subscription stops future billing cycles but does <strong data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1060\">not<\/strong> retroactively refund charges for any period during which the service was available or used.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1373\">\n<p data-start=\"1157\" data-end=\"1373\">If a subscription is canceled before the next billing date, access will remain available until the end of the current billing period. After this period, access will be discontinued unless the subscription is renewed.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1378\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1380\" data-end=\"1399\"><strong data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1397\">4. Refunds<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1400\" data-end=\"1517\"><strong data-start=\"1400\" data-end=\"1418\">Refund Policy:<\/strong> We generally provide services on a non-refundable basis following the initiation of service use.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1794\"><strong data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1532\">Question:<\/strong> Can I request a refund?<br data-start=\"1556\" data-end=\"1559\" \/><strong data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1570\">Answer:<\/strong> Refunds might be considered on a case-by-case basis for issues related to double billing or unauthorized charges. Requests should be made within <strong data-start=\"1716\" data-end=\"1727\">14 days<\/strong> of the transaction date. All decisions are at our sole discretion.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1796\" data-end=\"1799\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1801\" data-end=\"1832\"><strong data-start=\"1804\" data-end=\"1830\">5. Account Termination<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1833\" data-end=\"1978\">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account and refuse any and all current or future use of our service for any reason at any time.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"1980\" data-end=\"1983\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2006\"><strong data-start=\"1988\" data-end=\"2004\">6. Liability<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2007\" data-end=\"2132\">Our liability for the services provided under these Terms is limited to the greatest extent permissible under applicable law.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2134\" data-end=\"2137\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2139\" data-end=\"2167\"><strong data-start=\"2142\" data-end=\"2165\">7. Changes to Terms<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2168\" data-end=\"2355\">We may modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective upon posting on our site. Continued use of the service after changes are posted signifies your agreement to those changes.<\/p>\n<hr data-start=\"2357\" data-end=\"2360\" \/>\n<h2 data-start=\"2362\" data-end=\"2389\"><strong data-start=\"2365\" data-end=\"2387\">8. Account Sharing<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2391\" data-end=\"2420\"><strong data-start=\"2391\" data-end=\"2418\">Prohibition on Sharing:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2421\" data-end=\"2779\">\n<li data-start=\"2421\" data-end=\"2558\">\n<p data-start=\"2423\" data-end=\"2558\">The services provided through Fakedash are licensed to you for your individual or organizational use, depending on your account type.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2559\" data-end=\"2779\">\n<p data-start=\"2561\" data-end=\"2779\">Account sharing is strictly forbidden. You may <strong data-start=\"2608\" data-end=\"2615\">not<\/strong> share your login credentials or grant access to your account to anyone else, regardless of whether they are within your personal, familial, or professional circle.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2796\"><strong data-start=\"2781\" data-end=\"2794\">Security:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2797\" data-end=\"3076\">\n<li data-start=\"2797\" data-end=\"2852\">\n<p data-start=\"2799\" data-end=\"2852\">Keeping your account secure is your responsibility.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n